ing-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may.html\/#Tu_van_ve_dich_vu_cham_soc_noi_dung_website_cong_ty_nganh_dien_may\" title=\"T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y\">T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may.html\/#Cham_soc_noi_dung_website_cong_ty_nganh_dien_may_vai_tro_gi\" title=\"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y vai tr\u00f2 g\u00ec\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y vai tr\u00f2 g\u00ec<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may.html\/#Mot_so_cong_ty_hoat_dong_trong_linh_vuc_dien_may_hien_nay\" title=\"M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng ty ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y hi\u1ec7n nay\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng ty ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y hi\u1ec7n nay<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may.html\/#Quy_trinh_dich_vu_cham_soc_noi_dung_website_cong_ty_nganh_dien_may_cua_A_Chau_Media\" title=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media\">Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may.html\/#1_Phan_tich_yeu_cau\" title=\"1. Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch y\u00eau c\u1ea7u\">1. Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch y\u00eau c\u1ea7u<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may.html\/#2_Lap_ke_hoach\" title=\"2. L\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch\u00a0\">2. L\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may.html\/#3_Quan_tri_va_Marketing\" title=\"3. Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 Marketing\">3. Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 Marketing<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may.html\/#4_Bao_cao_khach_hang\" title=\"4. B\u00e1o c\u00e1o kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng\">4. B\u00e1o c\u00e1o kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may.html\/#Chon_dich_vu_cham_soc_noi_dung_website_cong_ty_nganh_dien_may_nao_uy_tin_hien_nay\" title=\"Ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y n\u00e0o uy t\u00edn hi\u1ec7n nay?\">Ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y n\u00e0o uy t\u00edn hi\u1ec7n nay?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y<\/strong>, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f4ng ty hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u1eady b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y n\u00f3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft hay kh\u00f4ng? V\u00e0 b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y? Quy tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ra sao? \u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, h\u00f4m nay <a href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/\"><strong>Achaumedia<\/strong><\/a> s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chi ti\u1ebft ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11345\" src=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-300x90.jpg\" alt=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"241\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-300x90.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-1024x308.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-768x231.jpg 768w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may.jpg 1349w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tu_van_ve_dich_vu_cham_soc_noi_dung_website_cong_ty_nganh_dien_may\"><\/span><strong>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t website. C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 website ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, \u0111em l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng mong mu\u1ed1n.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cham_soc_noi_dung_website_cong_ty_nganh_dien_may_vai_tro_gi\"><\/span><strong>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y vai tr\u00f2 g\u00ec<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n nay, ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kinh doanh h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. S\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u1eefa, m\u00e0 c\u00e1i quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ee7 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nhi\u1ec1u th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1eafng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, seo v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c vwebsite \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfm th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb kinh doanh n\u00e0o. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y t\u1ed1t, l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ty, h\u00e0ng nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p b\u1ea1n. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch t\u1eeb internet th\u00ec s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u201cb\u00f3p n\u00e1t\u201d. D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y\u00a0 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed, th\u1eddi gian r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11344\" src=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-3-300x228.png\" alt=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"607\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-3-300x228.png 300w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-3.png 609w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mot_so_cong_ty_hoat_dong_trong_linh_vuc_dien_may_hien_nay\"><\/span><strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng ty ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y hi\u1ec7n nay<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Th\u1ebf Gi\u1edbi Di \u0110\u1ed9ng; C\u00f4ng ty c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Media Mart Vi\u1ec7t Nam; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng si\u00eau th\u1ecb Th\u1ebf Gi\u1edbi Di \u0110\u1ed9ng; C\u00f4ng ty TNHH Cao Phong; Si\u00eau th\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y PICO; Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y Digicity; Ebest \u2013 C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH Ebest; M\u00e1y Ph\u00e1t \u0110i\u1ec7n Ho\u00e0ng Long \u2013 C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n \u0110i\u1ec7n M\u00e1y Ho\u00e0ng Long; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH TM DV M\u1ea1nh Nguy\u1ec5n; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH \u0110\u1ea7u T\u01b0 Ph\u00e1t Tri\u1ec3n Probuy; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH \u0110\u1ea7u T\u01b0 Th\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1i V\u00e0 Ph\u00e1t Tri\u1ec3n C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 Th\u00e0nh Ph\u00e1t; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH \u0110i\u1ec7n L\u1ea1nh Ng\u1ecdc Nguy\u00ean Ch\u00e2u; C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 F5; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH Th\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1i V\u00e0 XNK Prosell Vi\u1ec7t Nam;&#8230;.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00f4ng Ty CP AAC Th\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1i &amp; D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5 Qu\u1ed1c T\u1ebf; C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n MSGT; C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n SPC Vi\u1ec7t Nam; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH Th\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1i V\u00e0 Xu\u1ea5t Nh\u1eadp Kh\u1ea9u T\u00e2n \u0110\u00f4; C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n OTB Vi\u1ec7t Nam; C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n \u0110i\u1ec7n M\u00e1y Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecbnh; C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n Th\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1i V\u00e0 D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5 L\u1eadp Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng; Chi nh\u00e1nh C\u00f4ng Ty CP TM Nguy\u1ec5n Kim \u2013 Trung T\u00e2m Kinh Doanh T\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p Nguy\u1ec5n Kim H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i; C\u00f4ng ty TNHH MTV Th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u00e0nh; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH TM V\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea7u T\u01b0 Th\u00e0nh Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 M\u00e1y Vi\u1ec7t Trung; C\u00f4ng Ty TNHH M\u1ed9t Th\u00e0nh Vi\u00ean Th\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1i D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5 Tr\u00e0ng Thi;,&#8230;..<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_dich_vu_cham_soc_noi_dung_website_cong_ty_nganh_dien_may_cua_A_Chau_Media\"><\/span><strong>Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 quy tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng theo chu\u1ea9n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m lu\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 l\u00e0m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Phan_tich_yeu_cau\"><\/span><strong>1. Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch y\u00eau c\u1ea7u<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eafm r\u00f5 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1eeb t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p. M\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n t\u00f3m t\u1eaft v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n, do \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e0ng chi ti\u1ebft c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Lap_ke_hoach\"><\/span><strong>2. L\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y\u00a0 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed, th\u1eddi gian r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi ti\u1ebft cho c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c nh\u01b0 bi\u00ean so\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i dung, x\u1eed l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft l\u00ean website v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u1edbi KPIs r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u01a1 s\u1edf nghi\u1ec7m thu \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9nh trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5\u00a0 nh\u1eb1m mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao nh\u1ea5t cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Quan_tri_va_Marketing\"><\/span><strong>3. Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 Marketing<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung website \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi copywriter, designer, marketer. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n h\u00f3a cao n\u00ean chi ph\u00ed th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u1ea5p nh\u01b0ng mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Bao_cao_khach_hang\"><\/span><strong>4. B\u00e1o c\u00e1o kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea v\u00e0 b\u00e1o c\u00e1o qua email c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1-5 h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a website, b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c b\u00e1o c\u00e1o tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 do Google ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nh\u01b0 Google Analytics, Google webmaster.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11342\" src=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-1-300x157.png\" alt=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"419\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-1-300x157.png 300w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-1-1024x536.png 1024w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-1-768x402.png 768w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/dich-vu-cham-soc-noi-dung-website-cong-ty-nganh-dien-may-1.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chon_dich_vu_cham_soc_noi_dung_website_cong_ty_nganh_dien_may_nao_uy_tin_hien_nay\"><\/span><strong>Ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y n\u00e0o uy t\u00edn hi\u1ec7n nay?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m, l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c uy t\u00edn v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media l\u00e0 doanh nghi\u1ec7p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng tin. Hi\u1ec7n nay, \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u1edbn trong c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0: Viettel, B\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ICANN\u2026 \u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u00e0y cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 uy t\u00edn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website.<\/p>\n<p>L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty chuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00ean ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, d\u1ec5 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u0103m s\u00f3c web \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media n\u00ean d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u d\u00f9ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y, h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 quay phim ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh, <a href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/san-xuat-phim-quang-cao-chuyen-nghiep\/\"><strong>s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t phim qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong><\/a>, doanh nghi\u1ec7p, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o online,&#8230;\u00a0 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nh\u00e9<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c n\u1ed9i dung website c\u00f4ng ty ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u00e1y, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f4ng ty hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u1eady b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y n\u00f3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft hay kh\u00f4ng? V\u00e0 b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y? Quy tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ra sao? \u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected"